MySQL Workbench?: MySQL Workbench is a professional visual tool used by developers, data engineers, analysts, and DBAs to design, develop, test, optimize, and manage MySQL databases
Inkaa Simplega MySQL Workbench = Control Center of MySQL Databases

Why Companies Use MySQL Workbench(SPARK Cheptharu)

 Feature             Industry Benefit          
 SQL Editor        | Write & execute queries,Debug, Optimize   
 Schema Designer   | Design databases visually
 ER Diagram        | Visualize relationships, Create table relationships, Build chemas 
 Server Monitoring | Check performance( Manage users, Monitor performance, Backup databases, Restore databases),Configure server settings         
 User Management   | Control access            
 Backup & Restore  | Data protection           
Without Workbench -> Managing databases becomes slow and risky

